		<title>Mayo Clinic Minute: Does thyroid cancer affect women more than men?</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-minute-does-thyroid-cancer-affect-women-more-than-men/</link>
		
